ates calendar events for court hearings with reminders at 1 day and 1 hour before. Deduplicates by case number + hearing time.\n\n5. **Local Database** -- Persists all SMS records and downloaded PDFs in a Room database with MD5-based deduplication for documents.\n\n---\n\n### Directory Structure\n\n```\nCourtAssistant/\n├── build.gradle.kts                  # Root build config (AGP 8.2.2, Kotlin 1.9.22, KSP)\n├── settings.gradle.kts               # Project settings\n├── gradle.properties                 # JVM args (8GB heap), AndroidX enabled\n├── gradlew.bat                       # Gradle wrapper (Windows)\n├── local.properties                  # Local SDK path\n├── add-to-calendar.patch             # Empty patch file\n├── java_pid*.hprof                   # 3 heap dump files (~1.7GB total, likely debug artifacts)\n└── app/\n    ├── build.gradle.kts              # App module: Compose, Room, iText, ML Kit, OkHttp\n    ├── proguard-rules.pro\n    └── src/main/\n        ├── AndroidManifest.xml       # Permissions: SMS, Calendar, Internet\n        ├── res/                      # Drawables, strings, themes, file_paths.xml\n        └── java/com/court/assistant/\n            ├── CourtApp.kt           # Application class (lazy DB + Repository init)\n            ├── MainActivity.kt       # Entry point, permission handling, Compose setup\n            ├── calendar/\n            │   └── CalendarSync.kt   # Calendar event creation with dedup + reminders\n            ├── data/\n            │   ├── db/\n            │   │   ├── CourtDao.kt          # Room DAO (SMS + PDF CRUD)\n            │   │   ├── CourtDatabase.kt     # Room DB v2 with migration\n            │   │   ├── CourtSmsEntity.kt    # SMS table entity\n            │   │   └── PdfDocumentEntity.kt # PDF table entity (MD5 unique index)\n            │   └── repository/\n            │       └── CourtRepository.kt   # Repository layer\n            ├── pdf/\n            │   ├── PdfDownloadManager.kt    # OkHttp downloader with cookie support + MD5\n            │   └── PdfParser.kt             # iText + ML Kit OCR, extracts SubpoenaInfo\n            ├── sms/\n            │   ├── SmsParser.kt             # Regex-based SMS field extraction\n            │   └── SmsReader.kt             # ContentResolver SMS reader with keyword filter\n            ├── ui/\n            │   ├── MainScreen.kt            # SMS list with expandable cards\n            │   ├── Navigation.kt            # NavHost: main -> webview -> pdf preview\n            │   ├── PdfPreviewScreen.kt      # PDF renderer with hearing info card\n            │   ├── WebViewScreen.kt         # Embedded browser with auto PDF interception\n            │   └── theme/\n            │       ├── Theme.kt             # \"Song Dynasty aesthetic\" color scheme\n            │       └── Type.kt              # Serif typography\n            ├── utils/\n            │   └── Md5Util.kt               # File MD5 calculation\n            ├── viewmodel/\n            │   └── MainViewModel.kt         # Central ViewModel: SMS load, PDF download, calendar sync\n            └── webview/\n                └── CourtWebViewClient.kt    # Intercepts PDF URLs in WebView\n```\n\n---\n\n### Key Dependencies\n\n| Library | Purpose |\n|---|---|\n| Jetpack Compose + Material 3 | UI framework |\n| Room 2.6.1 | Local SQLite database |\n| iText 7.2.5 | PDF text extraction |\n| ML Kit Chinese OCR | Fallback OCR for scanned PDFs |\n| OkHttp 4.12 | PDF downloading |\n| Navigation Compose | Screen navigation |\n\n### Design Notes\n\n- The UI uses a custom \"Song Dynasty aesthetic\" (宋氏美学) theme with colors like Ivory, Cinnabar Red, Jade Green, and Amber Gold, with serif typography throughout.\n- The footer credits \"宋氏美学，单夫纯律师制作保留权利\" (Song aesthetic, rights reserved by lawyer Dan Fuchun).\n- The 3 `.hprof` heap dump files in the root are ~1.7GB combined and are debug artifacts that should likely be cleaned up.","type":"text"}],"totalDurationMs":108060,"totalTokens":26051,"totalT