{"parentUuid":"0de7186e-2163-4a63-970b-3369085885a3","isSidechain":false,"userType":"external","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Administrator","sessionId":"a4e11369-bc15-4ff1-9b18-115fc4dd0659","version":"2.1.41","gitBranch":"HEAD","slug":"buzzing-wobbling-rossum","message":{"content":[{"text":"\n\n好的，我已经看完了所有代码。现在来总结发现的问题并完成所有修复。\n\n## 已完成的修复\n\n### 1. SmsParser.kt — 短信时间解析（已修复）\n- 正则增加了对\"上午/下午\"、\"分\"字后缀的支持\n- `parseHearingTime` 增加了下午时间 +12 小时的逻辑\n\n### 2. PdfParser.kt — PDF传票解析（已修复）\n- `location` 正则增加了\"应到处所\"匹配（原来只有\"应到地点\"）\n- 时间正则同样增加了\"上午/下午\"和\"分\"字支持\n- 补全了缺失的 `caseType` 参数\n\n## 还需修复\n\n### 3. WebView PDF链接点击无反应\n\n看了 `CourtWebViewClient.kt`，问题在于 `shouldOverrideUrlLoading` 只拦截导航类的 URL 跳转。但有些法院网页的 PDF 链接是通过 JavaScript 触发的（如 `window.open()`、`blob:` URL、或动态 `<a>` 标签点击），这些不会触发 `shouldOverrideUrlLoading`。虽然已有 `setDownloadListener`，但某些服务器返回的 PDF 响应头没有 `Content-Disposition`，也没有 `.pdf` 扩展名，导致 WebView 既不触发导航拦截也不触发下载监听。\n\n让我增强拦截逻辑：","type":"text"}],"id":"msg_20260213153346","model":"claude-opus-4-6","role":"assistant","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"type":"message","usage":{"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":35774,"input_tokens":2394,"output_tokens":1}},"type":"assistant","uuid":"7f6e70c4-dc81-4bf8-9748-a7b98917a74a","timestamp":"2026-02-13T15:33:57.741Z"}
{"type":"file-history-snapshot","messageId":"08d02cff-1c9a-4d5a-9549-d11415b49936","snapshot":{"messageId":"90ed467a-e204-4ace-8a89-d81a7c6f95f3","trackedFileBackups":{"Desktop\\CourtAssistant\\app\\src\\main\\java\\com\\court\\assistant\\sms\\SmsParser.kt":{"backupFileName":"8c5824fcb73475e5@v1","version":1,"backupTime":"2026-02-13T15:33:04.848Z"},"Desktop\\CourtAssistant\\app\\src\\main\\java\\com\\court\\assistant\\pdf\\PdfParser.kt":{"backupFileName":"6f9be4ab476039bc@v1","version":1,"backupTime":"2026-02-13T15:33:20.938Z"},"Desktop\\CourtAssistant\\app\\src\\main\\java\\com\\court\\assistant\\webview\\CourtWebViewClient.kt":{"backupFileName":"e316416f7bec0000@v1","version":1,"backupTime":"2026-02-13T15:34:07.686Z"}},"timestamp":"2026-02-13T15:30:28.228Z"},"isSnapshotUpdate":true}
{"parentUuid":"7f6e70c4-dc81-4bf8-9748-a7b98917a74a","isSidechain":false,"userType":"external","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Administrator","sessionId":"a4e11369-bc15-4ff1-9b18-115fc4dd0659","version":"2.1.41","gitBranch":"HEAD","slug":"buzzing-wobbling-rossum","message":{"content":[{"id":"tooluse_Sl6MUSv6S5tLwSH6Axcocm","input":{"replace_all":false,"file_path":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\Desktop\\CourtAssistant\\app\\src\\main\\java\\com\\court\\assistant\\webview\\CourtWebViewClient.kt","old_string":"package com.court.assistant.webview\n\nimport android.webkit.WebResourceRequest\nimport android.webkit.WebView\nimport android.webkit.WebViewClient\n\nclass CourtWebViewClient(\n    private val onPdfDetected: (url: String) -> Unit,\n    private val onPageLoaded: () -> Unit\n) : WebViewClient() {\n\n    override fun shouldOverrideUrlLoading(view: WebView?, request: WebResourceRequest?): Boolean {\n        val url = request?.url?.toString() ?: return false\n        if (isPdfUrl(url)) {\n            onPdfDetected(url)\n            return true\n        }\n        return false\n    }\n\n    override fun onPageFinished(view: WebView?, url: String?) {\n        super.onPageFinished(view, url)\n        onPageLoaded()\n    }\n\n    private fun isPdfUrl(url: String): Boolean {\n        val lower = url.lowercase()\n        return lower.endsWith(\".pdf\") || lower.contains(\".pdf?\") || lower.contains(\"getpdf\")\n    }\n}","new_string":"package com.court.assistant.webview\n\nimport android.webkit.WebResourceRequest\nimport android.webkit.WebResourceResponse\nimport android.webkit.WebView\nimport android.webkit.WebViewClient\n\nclass CourtWebViewClient(\n    private val onPdfDetected: (url: String) -> Unit,\n    private val onPageLoaded: () -> Unit\n) : WebViewClient() {\n\n    override fun shouldOverrideUrlLoading(view: WebView?, request: WebResourceRequest?): Boolean {\n        val url = request?.url?.toString() ?: return false\n        if (isPdfUrl(url)) {\n            onPdfDetected(url)\n            return true\n        }\n        return false\n    }\n\n    override fun shouldInterceptRequest(view: WebView?, request: WebResourceRequest?): WebResourceResponse? {\n        val url = request?.url?.toString() ?: return null\n        // 拦截通过 XHR/fetch 等方式请求的 PDF URL\n        if (isPdfUrl(url) && request.method.equals(\"GET\", ignoreCase = true)) {\n            view?.post { onPdfDetected(url) }\n            return null\n        }\n        return null\n    }\n\n    override fun onPageFinished(view: WebView?, url: String?) {\n        super.onPageFinished(view, url)\n        onPageLoaded()\n        // 注入JS：拦截通过 window.open 或 JS 触发的 PDF 链接\n        view?.evaluateJavascript(\"\"\"\n            (function() {\n                if (window._courtPdfHooked) return;\n                window._courtPdfHooked = true;\n                document.addEventListener('click', function(e) {\n                    var el = e.target;\n                    while (el && el.tagName !== 'A') el = el.parentElement;\n                    if (el && el.href) {\n                        var href = el.href.toLowerCase();\n                        if (href.endsWith('.pdf') || href.indexOf('.pdf?') !== -1\n                            || href.indexOf('getpdf') !== -1 || href.indexOf('download') !== -1\n                            || href.indexOf('文书') !== -1) {\n                            window.location.href = el.href;\n                        }\n                    }\n                }, true);\n                var origOpen = window.open;\n                window.open = function(url) {\n                    if (url) window.location.href = url;\n                    return null;\n                };\n            })();\n        \"\"\".trimIndent(), null)\n    }\n\n    private fun isPdfUrl(url: String): Boolean {\n        val lower = url.lowercase()\n        return lower.endsWith(\".pdf\") || lower.contains(\".pdf?\")\n            || lower.contains(\"getpdf\") || lower.contains(\"download\") && lower.contains(\"pdf\")\n    }\n}"},"name":"Edit","type":"tool_use"}],"id":"msg_20260213153346","model":"claude-opus-4-6","role":"assistant","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"type":"message","usage":{"input_tokens":2394,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":35774,"output_tokens":1874,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"type":"assistant","uuid":"08d02cff-1c9a-4d5a-9549-d11415b49936","timestamp":"2026-02-13T15:34:07.655Z"}
