{"parentUuid":"c4c194ff-3eeb-4ebf-a5c2-60225c489f89","isSidechain":false,"userType":"external","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Administrator","sessionId":"a4e11369-bc15-4ff1-9b18-115fc4dd0659","version":"2.1.41","gitBranch":"HEAD","slug":"buzzing-wobbling-rossum","message":{"content":[{"text":"\n\n问题找到了。`loadSms()` 中第63行 `if (repo.smsExists(hash)) continue` —— 短信已经在数据库中了（之前旧版本已经读取过），所以整个解析和日历同步逻辑被跳过了。\n\n也就是说：\n1. 旧版本读取短信 → 解析时间错误 → 写入错误的日历事件\n2. 新版本读取短信 → 发现短信已存在（hash相同）→ 直接跳过 → 不会重新同步日历\n\n解决方案：需要对已存在的短信也重新解析并同步日历（当 `calendarEventId` 为空时）。","type":"text"}],"id":"msg_20260213155635","model":"claude-opus-4-6","role":"assistant","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"type":"message","usage":{"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":80679,"input_tokens":383,"output_tokens":1}},"type":"assistant","uuid":"2e66b6bc-f2c4-4f21-9fa5-de45e40267ef","timestamp":"2026-02-13T15:56:41.955Z"}
